doctype html
html
	head
		title gitmoji | 关于 | git 提交信息的 emoji 指南
		link(rel="canonical", href="https://gitmoji.carloscuesta.me/about")
		style
			include ../../dist/css/style.css
		include _includes/_meta.pug
	body
		include _includes/_icons.pug
		include _includes/_nav.pug
		header.header
			include ../images/gitmoji.svg
			h2 git 提交信息的 emoji 指南
		main.wrap
			section
				h1 关于
				p #[strong Gitmoji 是一个 GitHub 提交信息的 emoji 指南]。致力于成为一个标准化的备忘单 —— 在 GitHub 提交信息上使用 #[a(href="http://emoji.muan.co") emoji] 的指南。
				p 在#[strong 提交信息]时#[strong 使用 emoji]提供了一种#[strong 简单的方式]来#[strong 识别提交的目的和意图]，只需要看一眼所使用的 emoji 就好了。因为有很多的 emoji，所以创建一份指南来让使用 emoji 变得轻松这件事就很有必要了。
				p 本项目开源，这意味着所有人都能参与、提建议、讨论和添加新的 emoji。请参考#[a(href="#contributing-gitmoji") 贡献部分] 以及这份#[a(href="https://github.com/jeff-tian/gitmoji/blob/master/.github/CONTRIBUTING.md") 贡献指南].
				div
					a.btn.btn-pink(href="https://github.com/jeff-tian/gitmoji/")
						svg.icon.icon-star
							use(xlink:href='#icon-star')
						| GitHub
					a.btn.btn-pink(href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=gitmoji%20-%20%40zizhujy%20%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84%20git%20%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E7%9A%84%20%23emoji%20%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%E3%80%82&url=https://gitmoji.js.org", target="_blank")
						svg.icon.icon-twitter
							use(xlink:href='#icon-twitter')
						| 推特
			section
				h1 Using gitmoji with #[a(href="https://github.com/jeff-tian/gitmoji-cli") gitmoji-cli]
				p An easy solution for using gitmoji from your command line, is to install #[a(href="https://github.com/jeff-tian/gitmoji-cli") gitmoji-cli]. A gitmoji interactive client for using emojis on commit messages.
				pre
					code $ npm i -g gitmoji-cli
			section
				h1#contributing-gitmoji Contributing to gitmoji
				p Contributing to gitmoji it's a piece of cake 🍰! This project it's a static website built with #[i Pug, SCSS, Gulp and ES6]. All the gitmojis displayed are rendered from a JSON file. Before submitting any pull request, please follow the next steps:
				ol
					li #[a(href="https://github.com/jeff-tian/gitmoji/issues/new") Create an issue] filling the template.
					li After discussing the idea, feature or suggestion, #[a(href="https://github.com/jeff-tian/gitmoji/fork") fork gitmoji]
					li Create a new branch with the feature name. (Eg: add-emoji-deploy, fix-website-header)
					li Make your changes and send a #[a(href="https://help.github.com/articles/creating-a-pull-request/") pull request ].
				div
					a.btn.btn-pink(href="https://github.com/jeff-tian/gitmoji/blob/master/.github/CONTRIBUTING.md") Contributing guidelines

		include _includes/_footer.pug
	script
		include ../scripts/main.js
